div.div:
Cap side panel width at 2/3 browser width while respecting min width
For normal sized browser windows this means that the side panel will not resize larger than 2/3 the browser width. For narrow browser windows where 2/3 the browser width would be less than the side panel's minimum width, the side panel won't go below the minimum width. This cl also adds more comprehensive test coverage.
