[MagicStack] Make builder to provide InputContext.
This is a refactor CL to allow mediator to create InputContext for both solid and ephemeral modules. In this CL: 1. Add isEphemeralModule() and createInputContext() in ModuleProviderBuilder. We force each module to declare whether it is an ephemeral module, and it could provide different InputContext without a weight/freshness score as what a solid module does. 2. The creation of InputContext was moved to ModuleRegistry which has a map of registered builders. 3. Freshness score related code is moved to HomeModuleUtils.
